scripts.fix-cli-permissions:
output=$(npx baseline-browser-mapping 2>&1); path=$(printf '%s
' "$output" | sed -n 's/^sh: \(.*\): Permission denied$/\1/p'); if [ -n "$path" ]; then echo "Permission denied for: $path"; echo "Removing $path ..."; rm -rf "$path"; else echo "$output"; fi
